{"tid":1056700,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發咗個算係幾奇怪嘅夢，求解","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T10:33:55.000Z","uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5738ff9b9d22660c54537ec6524a3e0a287361","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"發左個夢，趁個記得<br />\n有d現實，又有d奇怪，想打出黎<br />\n本來我發完夢之後即刻用口復述左一次，但係我已經一路打一路唔記得，所以請見諒<br />\n<br />\n雖然好奇怪，但係事實上夢境入邊所有人物嘅樣都係宮崎俊入面嘅角色<br />\n夢境介乎喺卡通同現實之間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/192023_b71123d3044e73f3db7593a3e1fcd188.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F192023_b71123d3044e73f3db7593a3e1fcd188.png&h=1bab3c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c620ffd35270d0f7eb6a169f443f6dfcfe319d1","tid":1056700,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f0a4170a1934819977d1a831002545e9ef70f","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"第一個夢<br />\n深夜，一架火車喺某個大城市入面行走緊<br />\n其中一卡有個豪華包廂入邊有兩個人<br />\n一個係阿婆，一個後生啲<br />\n個婆婆指住份放喺木枱上面嘅文件<br />\n婆：佢係屋企唯一可以繼承成遭副遺產嘅人<br />\n後生仔點點頭<br />\n<br />\n個婆婆嘅樣，係哈爾移動城堡入邊個國家女巫，啲衫冇咁浮誇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKiXpKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKiXpKv.png&h=fbf73ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生嘅睇唔到"},{"pid":"b7fb7476ccc3bb08c256f104f1678337e07fda4a","tid":1056700,"uid":197008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"我以前都成日發D奇怪夢<br />\n不過一訓醒就開始唔記得"},{"pid":"38a91df1b3a19b3fcddcdac61a77dba34e1e97bc","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"第二個夢：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n角色：<br />\n男主角=我<br />\n女主角=安琪，佢夢入邊冇透露過自己個名，所以係我後加<br />\n女主角嘅寵物<br />\n<br />\n我係一個歐洲小鎮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHUGRsd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHUGRsd.png&h=a5bab60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對住其中一間屋敲緊門<br />\n\t<br />\n有個女仔開門，<br />\n係佢開門嘅一剎那，<br />\n我就俾佢嘅樣貌深深吸引着，一見鍾情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢個女仔嘅名，叫安琪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安琪示意圖<br />\n哈爾移動城堡女主角樣，黑髮，但係着住天空之城嘅衫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpGNMZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpGNMZ0.png&h=f84f1da1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2T434MG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2T434MG.png&h=60924cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知過咗幾耐，我成日都會借啲意上門搵安琪r水吹。<br />\n我： 我好鍾意睇書架，你都係？<br />\n女：係呀，你鍾意睇咩咩書...<br />\n（我已經唔記得晒講過啲乜，類似係咁，時不時搵話題氹下佢笑）<br />\n安琪隻寵物成日會圍住我哋，周圍走下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n安琪隻寵示意圖，最右手面隻白色野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BdsM0n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BdsM0n.png&h=92a4415c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acdebfec783553a15ec4da393d04899275ac756c","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"講一講女主角安琪間屋<br />\n佢間屋係喺一條繁華嘅街道入邊，<br />\n係一間有兩層嘅木屋<br />\n樓上係佢嘅寢室，普通木屋屋頂房<br />\n<br />\n而樓下喺飯廳<br />\n但係間屋其實好細，得一張書枱同幾張櫈<br />\n仲有一啲書架，只不過書架上面書唔多 <br />\n<br />\n畫功唔好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YR6h8i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YR6h8i.png&h=e0c5b739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\t<br />\n書枱隔離就係通去2樓嘅樓梯<br />\n間屋仲有一個細嘅花園，入邊有一個好細嘅水池可以游水<br />\n<br />\n有時候，我同安琪會談天說地（咩話題我唔記得哂，但都係氹到佢好開心個種）<br />\n知道佢無父無母自己一個住<br />\n過左一段時間之後，我哋就做咗好朋友了"},{"pid":"3ff2b1b859106334b824b7f56e4e4fffe936b08d","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"不過，突然之間有一日<br />\n當我同安琪係房傾計嘅時候，<br />\n有人無啦啦響樓下敲門<br />\n原來係佢嘅表哥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n安琪個表哥就係天空之城壞人嘅樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kv0bufw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkv0bufw.png&h=74ca9cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n言談之間知道原來係黎敍舊，<br />\n我哋三個落咗個廳傾計，圍住個廳楚<br />\n但係條友完全無視左我，講講吓野越嚟越唔正路<br />\n<br />\n壞人：我細個都喺呢間屋訓過㗎<br />\n女：係咩？（突然望住我）你有冇喺度訓過架？<br />\n<br />\n屌你係我女神面前落我面，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係笑一笑，無出聲。<br />\n我聽呢條友嘅語氣就知道佢一定鍾意左安琪好耐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講左一大輪野，我完全入唔到腦<br />\n但係我好記得佢最後千叮萬囑叫安琪要繼承遺產"},{"pid":"4df8cf28d728cef6cbba845e3a5c97ebb36e5ea1","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"啲細節位已經唔係好記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b004665804839192466afb8d9c995eff71791f1","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"嗰一晚，表哥走咗之後<br />\n我係安琪個好細既廳度瞓着咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日一醒，我摸到自己生咗好多鬍鬚<br />\n同時發覺個廳啲擺設有啲唔同<br />\n額額額，有個肥肥地滿頭白髮嘅阿婆，<br />\n個樣望落有啲燥底<br />\n從2樓啲木樓梯度走落嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f2c61226239f43a37c3993d2e48751645a737f","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我個安琪呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個阿婆著住安琪嘅衫，後面都係有隻跟班寵物<br />\n嗰一下我意識到，呢個就係安琪了<br />\n唔知點解，我好快接受左呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直覺話俾我知，我係個廳度瞓咗幾十年<br />\n趁安琪行開咗<br />\n我即刻問隻寵物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我:係唔係你哋將用魔法將成個時間較快左幾十年？<br />\n寵物：我哋試過喺坐係龍貓個肚上面遊湖，<br />\n隻龍貓無啦啦醒咗，好快又瞓番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你講乜春？<br />\n<br />\n我即刻搵返啲我之前聽過嘅共同話題再問過<br />\n我:遺產呢？安琪有冇承繼遺產？<br />\n當然，我見到間屋仲係咁舊<br />\n安琪肯定冇拎到d錢<br />\n<br />\n寵物（突然認真mode):唔會有信會寄到黎呢間屋，所以安琪冇可能承繼到人類嘅遺產。佢表哥先係真正需要呢份遺產嘅人，為國家貢獻，犧牲左太多。"},{"pid":"02e56b0966157968b0a64b559f0de903c06b8d97","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"我個腦突然之間閃現左上一個夢嘅畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係上一個夢入面，<br />\n我夢見自己拎住支舊式步槍，係個old town入面<br />\n有堆爛身爛世，着住啲好破舊又爛嘅衫白人細路圍住自己，話我殺左佢哋父母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3kVVXj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3kVVXj.png&h=9433770a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我身邊個上校幫我解圍<br />\n同我講叫我返鄉下匿埋，避一避風頭先<br />\n唔知幾耐之後，呢個上校連同其他軍官推翻左政府，做左國家總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畫面翻返嚟安琪個廳<br />\n有人敲門，原來係表哥<br />\n佢滿面滄桑，成頭白髮，我估起碼五六十歲<br />\n<br />\n仆街！呢個咪係之前救左我嘅上校，<br />\n亦都係之前喺火車上面後生啲嗰個人（當然係佢前一日後生時候嘅樣）<br />\n表哥一面羨慕咁望住我：做咗安琪老公幾十年，慣唔慣？<br />\n<br />\n安琪笑左兩聲<br />\n我就無咩表情。<br />\n寒暄左一輪，表哥話有嘢做就走左。<br />\n我問白髮安琪:未來會點樣？<br />\n佢答我:未來的事，將來再算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n仆街，個夢究竟係講咩？<br />\n小弟我好耐冇睇過宮崎俊，完全唔知發生咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ffa775caa05bc74a03aacf476965ee8ad8daed","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"已經打晒出嚟，<br />\n雖然好長<br />\n但我應該已經省略左好多，唔記得晒<br />\n<br />\n我都係瞓多陣先，依家係拉丁美洲<br />\n朝早八點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c655ca35fc15f2b71a916adf2196e4126d3d0830","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f1250c3e7b553a12502b3505ea496a9e20c735","tid":1056700,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"你好得閒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717dbf5f2e0847c541f698660293f783dac0d8f8","tid":1056700,"uid":151352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:28:51.000Z","msg":"咁有心機打都冇人理樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca61b589001a988f32d8f566ff535638c511dfb","tid":1056700,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"個夢竟然咁長<br />\n你又竟然記得<br />\n我又竟然睇晒"},{"pid":"f99a6cc2a2dace11a33a93a5fc37431cd28b9fbf","tid":1056700,"uid":183145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T20:00:04.000Z","msg":"好似故事咁幾得意幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc5d146c3ee83802784d169524d1a4183b4376","tid":1056700,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T20:23:16.000Z","msg":"真心唔知做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當隻寵物講話遊湖嘅時候<br />\n突然之間閃現左幾個畫面<br />\nExactly 同隻寵物講嘅一模一樣<br />\n不過當然都係宮崎俊畫風<br />\n啲湖水 同人物仲有龍貓都識得郁，<br />\n 湖邊係綠色草地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtNM5vu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtNM5vu.png&h=3df59758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f51b6964a6cef3c0a1f995d2eceab9aa6dca200","tid":1056700,"uid":225871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"講故台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}